title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 10/06/2018
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 10/06/2018
description:
Coming off a 2-2-1 week Colin talks about his Blazing 5 picks with Fox Sports Radio Host and founder of pregame.com RJ Bell who tells him which ones the wise guys in Vegas like and dislike in this exclusive podcast. Plus, Colin reveals and extra bonus pick not included in his Blazing 5.
